Graph-JEPA Architecture
\f0\b0  is an\'a0 adaptation of Meta's V-JEPA 2 for tactical drone defense. Uses Graph Attention Network (GAT) layers instead of standard vision transformers to represent drone swarms as graphs. Includes a State Decoder for "Dream View" visualization (the AI shows you what it's imagining). This does not exist anywhere else.\cf0 \cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
