\f0\b0  is our COA generation engine with doctrine-aware reasoning, AAR learning loop, and V-JEPA integration. The advisor generates plans; the JEPA general war-games them in latent space.\cf0 \cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
JEPA Knowledge Base
\f0\b0  creates a neural bridge from OSINT text intelligence \uc0\u8594  128-dim context vectors \u8594  JEPA encoder injection. Grounds the world model in real-world intelligence. No other C-UAS system does this.\cf0 \cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
