\f0\b0  a three-tier rating system (Session/Global/AOR) that ensures perpetual AI improvement. This system (borrowed from chess) ensures our AI gets harder the better it gets. Our adversary AI escalates tactics (swarm attacks, pincer movements) as our defender improves. This is a closed-loop self-improvement engine.\cf0 \cb1 \
